msgid "POS API"
msgstr "POS API"

msgid "A valid POS license is required to access this endpoint."
msgstr "要訪問此端點，需要有效的 POS 授權證。"

msgid "POS access requires a staff account."
msgstr "POS 訪問需要員工帳號。"

msgid "You are not assigned to this terminal."
msgstr "您未被指派到這個終端機。"

#, python-format
msgid "You do not have permission: %(label)s."
msgstr "您沒有權限：%(label)s。"

msgid "Bundle variant selections: {bundle_item_id: variant_id}"
msgstr "捆包變體選擇：{bundle_item_id: variant_id}"

msgid "List of optional BundleItem IDs to exclude"
msgstr "可選排除的 BundleItem ID 清單"

msgid "Search by email, phone, or name"
msgstr "按電子郵件、電話或姓名搜索"

msgid "ID of the product to adjust stock for."
msgstr "要調整庫存的產品 ID。"

msgid "ID of the variant (required for variable products)."
msgstr "變體的 ID（變體產品需要）。"

msgid ""
"Type of adjustment: \"receive\" adds stock (e.g. new shipment), \"damage\" "
"removes stock (e.g. broken item), \"recount\" sets absolute on_hand count, "
"\"return\" adds stock back (e.g. customer return)."
msgstr ""
"調整類型：\"receive\" 增加庫存（例如新貨物），\"damage\" 減少庫存（例如損壞物品），\"recount\" 設置絕對的 "
"on_hand 數量，\"return\" 將庫存加回去（例如客戶退貨）。"

msgid ""
"For receive/return: units to add. For damage: units to remove. For recount: "
"new absolute on_hand count."
msgstr ""
"針對 receive/return：要增加的單位數。針對 damage：要移除的單位數。針對 recount：新的絕對 on_hand 數量。"

msgid "Required explanation for this adjustment (audit trail)."
msgstr "此調整所需的說明（審計軌跡）。"

msgid "Optional UUID for offline deduplication."
msgstr "用於離線去重的可選UUID。"

msgid "Signed quantity delta."
msgstr "已簽署的數量變化。"

msgid "Last four digits of card number (digits only)"
msgstr "信用卡號碼的最後四位（僅限數字）"

msgid "Amount to charge. If not provided, charges the full remaining balance."
msgstr "應收取的金額。如果不提供，則收取剩餘餘額的全部。"

msgid "Payment ID from the terminal provider (e.g. Stripe PaymentIntent ID)"
msgstr "來自終端提供商的付款 ID（例如 Stripe PaymentIntent ID）"

msgid "Provider-specific reader ID (e.g. Adyen POIID, Square device_id)"
msgstr "提供商特定的讀卡器 ID（例如 Adyen POIID、Square device_id）"

msgid "Provider-specific transaction ID for status polling"
msgstr "供應商特定交易 ID 用於狀態輪詢"

msgid ""
"Initial status -- typically \"pending\" for async providers, \"succeeded\" "
"for sync (Adyen)"
msgstr "初始狀態 -- 通常對於異步供應商為 \"pending\"，對於同步供應商 (Adyen) 為 \"succeeded\""

msgid "Current payment status"
msgstr "當前付款狀態"

msgid "Provider payment ID (when succeeded)"
msgstr "供應商付款ID（付款成功時）"

msgid "Reason for cancellation (when canceled)"
msgstr "取消原因（取消時）"

msgid "POS staff login"
msgstr "POS 員工登入"

msgid ""
"Authenticate a staff member for POS access. Returns access and refresh "
"tokens. Uses the same token system as the Admin API "
"(MobileTokenAuthentication)."
msgstr "為 POS 授權員工。返回存取和刷新令牌。使用與管理員 API 相同的令牌系統（MobileTokenAuthentication）。"

msgid "Login successful, returns tokens and terminal config"
msgstr "登入成功，返回令牌和終端配置"

msgid "Invalid credentials"
msgstr "憑證無效"

msgid "User is not a staff member"
msgstr "該使用者不是工作人員"

msgid "Refresh POS access token"
msgstr "重新整理 POS 存取權杖"

msgid "Exchange a refresh token for a new access token."
msgstr "以刷新令牌換取新的訪問令牌。"

msgid "New access token"
msgstr "新的存取權杖"

msgid "Invalid or expired refresh token"
msgstr "無效或已過期的重新整理權杖"

msgid "POS logout"
msgstr "POS 登出"

msgid "Invalidate the current access and refresh tokens."
msgstr "使目前的訪問令牌和刷新令牌失效。"

msgid "Logged out successfully"
msgstr "成功登出"

msgid "Get current POS cart"
msgstr "取得當前POS購物車"

msgid ""
"Returns the current cart for the authenticated cashier. Creates a new cart "
"if one does not exist. Requires staff authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr "返回已驗證收銀員的當前購物車。如果不存在購物車，則創建一個新的購物車。需要員工驗證和有效的 POS 授權。"

msgid "Add item to POS cart"
msgstr "將商品加入POS購物車"

msgid ""
"Add a product to the cashier's cart. Supports adding by product ID or "
"barcode. When barcode is provided without product_id, it resolves the "
"product automatically. Requires staff authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr ""
"將產品加入收銀員的購物車。支援透過產品 ID 或條碼添加。當提供條碼而未指定 product_id 時，系統會自動解析產品。需要員工驗證和有效的 POS"
" 授權。"

msgid "Invalid product, variant, or insufficient stock"
msgstr "無效的產品、變體或庫存不足"

msgid "Update cart item quantity"
msgstr "更新購物車商品數量"

msgid ""
"Update the quantity of a cart item. Set quantity to 0 to remove the item. "
"Requires staff authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr "更新購物車項目數量。將數量設為 0 可移除該項目。需要員工驗證和有效的 POS 授權。"

msgid "Invalid quantity or insufficient stock"
msgstr "數量無效或庫存不足"

msgid "Cart item not found"
msgstr "找不到購物車商品"

msgid "Remove item from cart"
msgstr "從購物車中移除項目"

msgid ""
"Remove a specific item from the cart. Requires staff authentication and "
"valid POS license."
msgstr "從購物車中移除特定商品。需要工作人員驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "Apply voucher to cart"
msgstr "將優惠券套用至購物車"

msgid ""
"Apply a voucher/discount code to the cart. Only one voucher can be active at"
" a time. Requires staff authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr "將優惠券/折扣碼套用至購物車。一次只能啟用一張優惠券。需要員工驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "Invalid or expired voucher code"
msgstr "無效或已過期的優惠券代碼"

msgid "Remove voucher from cart"
msgstr "從購物車中移除優惠券"

msgid ""
"Remove the applied voucher from the cart. Requires staff authentication and "
"valid POS license."
msgstr "從購物車中移除已套用的優惠券。需要工作人員驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "No voucher applied"
msgstr "未套用優惠券"

msgid "Apply gift card to cart"
msgstr "將禮品卡套用至購物車"

msgid ""
"Apply a gift card code to the cart to cover part or all of the total. "
"Requires staff authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr "將禮品卡碼套用至購物車，以支付總額的一部分或全部。需要員工驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "Invalid gift card or insufficient balance"
msgstr "無效禮品卡或餘額不足"

msgid "Clear all items from cart"
msgstr "清除購物車所有商品"

msgid ""
"Remove all items, vouchers, and gift cards from the cart. Requires staff "
"authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr "從購物車中移除所有商品、優惠券和禮品卡。需要員工驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "Apply manual discount to cart item"
msgstr "將手動折扣套用至購物車項目"

msgid ""
"Apply a staff manual discount to a specific cart item. Returns "
"requires_approval=true if the discount exceeds staff limits. Requires staff "
"authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr ""
"對購物車中的特定商品應用員工手動折扣。如果折扣超過員工限制，將返回 requires_approval=true。需要員工驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "Discount applied or requires approval"
msgstr "已套用折扣或需審批"

msgid "Invalid discount or not authorized"
msgstr "無效折扣或未經授權"

msgid "Remove manual discount from cart item"
msgstr "從購物車項目中移除手動折扣"

msgid ""
"Remove a staff manual discount from a specific cart item. Requires staff "
"authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr "從特定購物車項目中移除員工手動折扣。需要員工驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "Discount removed"
msgstr "已移除折扣"

msgid "Apply manual discount to cart"
msgstr "將手動折扣套用至購物車"

msgid ""
"Apply a staff manual discount to the entire cart. Returns "
"requires_approval=true if the discount exceeds staff limits. Requires staff "
"authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr ""
"將員工手動折扣套用至整個購物車。如果折扣超出員工限制，將返回requires_approval=true。需要員工驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "Remove manual discount from cart"
msgstr "從購物車移除手動折扣"

msgid ""
"Remove the staff manual discount from the cart. Requires staff "
"authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr "從購物車中移除員工手動折扣。需要員工驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "Verify manager PIN"
msgstr "驗證經理PIN"

msgid ""
"Verify if a PIN is valid for a manager who can approve discounts. Returns "
"the manager's name if valid. Requires staff authentication and valid POS "
"license."
msgstr "驗證管理員的PIN是否有效，該管理員可以批准折扣。如果有效，將返回管理員的姓名。需要員工驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "PIN verification result"
msgstr "PIN驗證結果"

msgid "Approve discount with manager PIN"
msgstr "使用經理PIN批准折扣"

msgid ""
"Apply a discount that exceeds staff limits with manager approval. Requires a"
" valid manager PIN to proceed. Requires staff authentication and valid POS "
"license."
msgstr "在管理員批准的情況下應用超過員工限制的折扣。需要有效的管理員PIN才能繼續。需要員工驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "Discount approved and applied"
msgstr "折扣已批准並套用"

msgid "Invalid PIN or discount parameters"
msgstr "無效的PIN或折扣參數"

msgid "Park current cart"
msgstr "停放當前購物車"

msgid ""
"Save the current cart state for later restoration. Used when a customer "
"needs to step away and another customer needs to be served. Requires staff "
"authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr "保存當前購物車狀態，以便稍後恢復。當顧客需要離開，而另一位顧客需要被服務時會使用此功能。需要員工驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "Cart parked successfully"
msgstr "購物車停放成功"

msgid "Cart is empty or cannot be parked"
msgstr "購物車為空或無法停放"

msgid "List parked carts"
msgstr "列出停放的購物車"

msgid ""
"Get all parked carts for the current terminal. Requires staff authentication"
" and valid POS license."
msgstr "獲取當前終端的所有停放購物車。需要員工驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "List of parked carts"
msgstr "停放購物車清單"

msgid "Restore parked cart"
msgstr "恢復停放的購物車"

msgid ""
"Restore a parked cart, replacing the current cart contents. The current cart"
" will be cleared before restoration. Requires staff authentication and valid"
" POS license."
msgstr "恢復停放的購物車，並取代當前購物車的內容。恢復前會先清除當前購物車。需要員工驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "Cart restored successfully"
msgstr "購物車已成功恢復"

msgid "Current cart is not empty"
msgstr "目前購物車不為空"

msgid "Parked cart not found"
msgstr "停放的購物車不存在"

msgid "Delete parked cart"
msgstr "刪除停放的購物車"

msgid ""
"Permanently delete a parked cart. This cannot be undone. Requires staff "
"authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr "永久刪除停放的購物車。此操作無法撤銷。需要員工驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "Parked cart deleted"
msgstr "已刪除停放的購物車"

msgid "List POS products"
msgstr "列出POS產品"

msgid ""
"Returns products available for in-store sale, filtered by sales channel. "
"Includes warehouse-specific stock levels when a terminal is identified. "
"Products with images appear first, ordered by per-warehouse popularity."
msgstr "返回可供門店銷售的產品，按銷售渠道過濾。當識別到終端時，會包含倉庫特定的庫存水平。帶有圖片的產品會優先顯示，並按每個倉庫的熱門程度排序。"

msgid "Search by name, SKU, or barcode"
msgstr "按名稱、SKU 或條碼搜索"

msgid "Filter by category ID"
msgstr "按分類ID篩選"

msgid "Warehouse for stock levels"
msgstr "用於庫存水準的倉庫"

msgid "Page number (default: 1)"
msgstr "頁碼（預設：1）"

msgid "Items per page (default: 50, max: 200)"
msgstr "每頁項目數（預設：50，最大：200）"

msgid "Get product detail"
msgstr "取得產品詳情"

msgid "Returns full product details including variants and warehouse stock."
msgstr "返回完整的產品詳情，包括變體和倉庫庫存。"

msgid "Barcode lookup"
msgstr "條碼查詢"

msgid ""
"Look up a product or variant by barcode. Fast, indexed lookup for scanning."
msgstr "透過條碼查找產品或變體。快速的索引查找，適用於掃描。"

msgid "No product found with this barcode"
msgstr "未找到此條碼的產品"

msgid "List categories"
msgstr "列出分類"

msgid "Returns the category tree for POS product navigation."
msgstr "返回用於 POS 產品導航的分類樹。"

msgid "Process cash payment"
msgstr "處理現金支付"

msgid ""
"Complete a POS transaction with cash payment. Validates that the amount "
"tendered covers the order total and calculates change. Creates an Order with"
" channel='pos' and a POSPayment record. Requires an open shift on the "
"terminal. Requires staff authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr ""
"使用現金完成 POS 交易。驗證提供的金額是否足以支付訂單總額並計算找零。創建一個 channel='pos' 的 Order 和一個 "
"POSPayment 記錄。需要終端機上有開啟的班次。需要員工驗證和有效的 POS 授權。"

msgid "Empty cart or insufficient cash tendered"
msgstr "購物車為空或現金支付不足"

msgid "Process card payment"
msgstr "處理信用卡支付"

msgid ""
"Complete a POS transaction with card payment. Card processing is assumed to "
"be handled by an external card terminal. This endpoint records the card "
"reference and last four digits. Requires an open shift on the terminal. "
"Requires staff authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr ""
"使用卡支付完成 POS 交易。假設卡片處理由外部卡終端機處理。此端點會記錄卡的參考編號和最後四位數字。需要終端機上有開啟的班次。需要員工驗證和有效的 "
"POS 授權。"

msgid "Empty cart"
msgstr "清空購物車"

msgid "Check gift card balance"
msgstr "查看禮品卡餘額"

msgid ""
"Check the balance of a gift card for POS checkout. Returns the current "
"balance if valid, or an error message if invalid. Requires staff "
"authentication."
msgstr "檢查禮品卡餘額以進行 POS 結帳。若禮品卡有效，則返回當前餘額；若無效，則返回錯誤訊息。需要員工認證。"

msgid "Gift card balance info"
msgstr "禮品卡餘額資訊"

msgid "Invalid gift card or missing code"
msgstr "無效禮品卡或缺少代碼"

msgid "Process gift card payment"
msgstr "處理禮品卡付款"

msgid ""
"Complete a POS transaction using a gift card. Validates the gift card has "
"sufficient balance. If the gift card balance is less than the order total, "
"use the split tender endpoint instead. Requires an open shift on the "
"terminal. Requires staff authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr ""
"使用禮品卡完成 POS 交易。驗證禮品卡是否有足夠餘額。如果禮品卡餘額少於訂單總額，請改用分段付款端點。需要終端機上有開啟的班次。需要員工認證和有效的 "
"POS 授權證。"

msgid "Empty cart, invalid gift card, or insufficient balance"
msgstr "購物車為空、無效禮品卡或餘額不足"

msgid "Process split tender payment"
msgstr "處理分段付款"

msgid ""
"Complete a POS transaction using multiple payment methods (split tender). "
"The total of all payments must cover the order total. Change is calculated "
"on the last cash payment if the total exceeds the order amount. Requires an "
"open shift on the terminal. Requires staff authentication and valid POS "
"license."
msgstr ""
"使用多種付款方式完成 POS "
"交易（分拆付款）。所有付款總額必須涵蓋訂單總額。若總額超過訂單金額，找零將根據最後一筆現金付款計算。需要終端機上有一個開啟的班次。需要員工驗證和有效的 "
"POS 授權證。"

msgid "Empty cart, invalid payments, or insufficient total"
msgstr "購物車為空、付款無效或總金額不足"

msgid "Process terminal card payment"
msgstr "處理終端卡付款"

msgid ""
"Complete a POS transaction with an integrated card terminal payment. The "
"frontend must have already collected payment via the terminal SDK and "
"obtained a provider_payment_id (e.g. Stripe PaymentIntent). This endpoint "
"verifies the payment succeeded before creating the order. Requires an open "
"shift on the terminal. Requires staff authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr ""
"使用整合式卡片終端機付款完成 POS 交易。前端必須已經透過終端機 SDK 收取付款並取得 provider_payment_id（例如 Stripe "
"PaymentIntent）。此端點會在建立訂單前驗證付款是否成功。需要終端機上有一個開啟的班次。需要員工驗證和有效的 POS 授權證。"

msgid "Empty cart or payment verification failed"
msgstr "購物車為空或付款驗證失敗"

msgid "Search customers"
msgstr "搜尋客戶"

msgid ""
"Search for customers by email, phone, first name, or last name. Returns up "
"to 20 matching results. Minimum 2 characters required. Requires staff "
"authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr "透過電子郵件、電話、名字或姓氏搜尋客戶。最多返回 20 個匹配結果。最少需要 2 個字元。需要員工驗證和有效的 POS 授權。"

msgid "Search query (email, phone, or name). Minimum 2 characters."
msgstr "搜尋條件（郵箱、電話或姓名）。最少 2 個字元。"

msgid "Search query too short"
msgstr "搜尋內容太短"

msgid "Create walk-in customer"
msgstr "建立臨時客戶"

msgid ""
"Create a new customer for a walk-in sale. If a customer with the given email"
" already exists, returns the existing customer instead of creating a "
"duplicate. Email is optional for truly anonymous walk-in customers. Requires"
" staff authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr ""
"為臨時走進來的客戶建立新客戶。如果已經存在具有給定電子郵件的客戶，則返回現有客戶，而不是建立重複客戶。對於真正匿名的臨時客戶，電子郵件是可選的。需要員工驗證和有效的"
" POS 授權。"

msgid "Existing customer found with this email"
msgstr "已找到使用此電子郵件的現有客戶"

msgid "Get customer details"
msgstr "取得客戶資料"

msgid ""
"Retrieve customer details including contact info and recent order history. "
"Requires staff authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr "取得客戶詳細資料，包括聯繫資訊和最近的訂單歷史。需要員工驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "List stock levels for warehouse"
msgstr "列出倉庫庫存水準"

msgid ""
"Returns paginated stock levels for the terminal's warehouse. Supports search"
" by product name or SKU and filtering for low-stock or no-stock items. "
"Requires staff authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr "返回終端倉庫的分頁庫存水準。支援按產品名稱或SKU搜尋，並過濾庫存不足或無庫存的項目。需要員工驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "Search by product name or SKU"
msgstr "按產品名稱或SKU搜索"

msgid "Only return items at or below low stock threshold"
msgstr "僅返回低於或等於低庫存閾值的項目"

msgid "Only return items with zero available stock"
msgstr "僅返回庫存為零的項目"

msgid "Warehouse not determined"
msgstr "未指定倉庫"

msgid "Get product stock detail"
msgstr "取得產品庫存詳情"

msgid ""
"Returns stock levels for a specific product in the terminal's warehouse, "
"including variant-level breakdown. Requires staff authentication and valid "
"POS license."
msgstr "返回終端倉庫中特定產品的庫存水準，包括變體層面的細分。需要員工驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "Check stock across all locations"
msgstr "檢查所有位置的庫存"

msgid ""
"Returns stock levels for a product across all warehouse locations. Useful "
"for checking if an out-of-stock item is available at another location. The "
"current terminal's warehouse is marked with is_current=true. Requires staff "
"authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr ""
"返回產品在所有倉庫位置的庫存水準。可用於檢查缺貨商品是否在其他位置有庫存。當前終端的倉庫會標記為 "
"is_current=true。需要員工驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "Adjust stock levels"
msgstr "調整庫存數量"

msgid ""
"Adjust stock for a product in the terminal's warehouse. Supports four "
"adjustment types: 'receive' (add stock from shipment), 'damage' (remove "
"damaged/lost stock), 'recount' (set absolute on_hand from physical count), "
"'return' (add stock back from customer return). Creates an immutable "
"StockMovement audit record. Requires staff authentication, valid POS "
"license, and pos_stock_adjustment permission."
msgstr ""
"調整終端倉庫中產品的庫存。支援四種調整類型：'receive'（從貨運中增加庫存）、'damage'（移除損壞/遺失的庫存）、'recount'（根據實際盤點設定絕對的"
" on_hand）、'return'（從客戶退貨中增加庫存）。會建立不可變的 StockMovement 審計記錄。需要員工驗證、有效的 POS 授權和"
" pos_stock_adjustment 權限。"

msgid "Stock adjusted successfully"
msgstr "庫存調整成功"

msgid "Validation error or warehouse not determined"
msgstr "驗證錯誤或倉庫未確定"

msgid "Permission denied or POS license required"
msgstr "權限被拒絕或需要POS許可證"

msgid "Product or stock item not found"
msgstr "產品或庫存項目未找到"

msgid "List stock movement history"
msgstr "列出庫存異動記錄"

msgid ""
"Returns paginated stock movement records for the terminal's warehouse. "
"Useful for auditing recent stock changes (adjustments, damage, recounts, "
"returns). Supports filtering by product and movement type. Requires staff "
"authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr ""
"返回終端倉庫的分頁庫存變動記錄。可用於審計最近的庫存更改（調整、損壞、重新盤點、退貨）。支援按產品和變動類型過濾。需要員工驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "Filter movements by product ID"
msgstr "按產品 ID 篩選異動"

msgid "Comma-separated movement types to include (e.g. 'damage,recount')"
msgstr "以逗號分隔要包含的庫存異動類型（例如：'damage,recount'）"

msgid "Items per page (default: 20, max: 100)"
msgstr "每頁項目數（預設：20，最大：100）"

msgid "Get customer loyalty info"
msgstr "取得客戶忠誠度資訊"

msgid ""
"Retrieve loyalty membership status, tier, and points balance for a customer."
" Returns `is_member: false` if the customer has no active loyalty "
"membership. Requires staff authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr ""
"獲取客戶的忠誠度會員狀態、等級和積分餘額。如果客戶沒有有效的忠誠度會員資格，則返回 `is_member: "
"false`。需要員工驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid ""
"Loyalty membership info. `is_member` indicates whether the customer has an "
"active membership. When true, includes `tier_name`, `tier_color`, and "
"`available_points`."
msgstr ""
"忠誠度會員資訊。`is_member` 表示客戶是否有活躍的會員資格。當為 true 時，包含 `tier_name`、`tier_color` 和 "
"`available_points`。"

msgid "Preview loyalty points for cart"
msgstr "預覽購物車忠誠度點數"

msgid ""
"Calculate the loyalty points a customer would earn for a given cart total. "
"Returns 0 if the customer has no active loyalty membership. Requires staff "
"authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr "計算客戶在給定購物車總額下可獲得的忠誠度積分。如果客戶沒有活躍的忠誠度會員資格，則返回 0。需要員工驗證和有效的 POS 授權。"

msgid "Cart total as a decimal string (e.g. '49.99'). Defaults to '0'."
msgstr "購物車總額作為小數字串（例如 '49.99'）。預設為 '0'。"

msgid ""
"Points preview. `points_preview` is the number of points the customer would "
"earn for the given cart total."
msgstr "積分預覽。`points_preview` 是客戶根據給定的購物車總額可賺取的積分數。"

msgid "List POS orders"
msgstr "列出POS訂單"

msgid ""
"Returns orders with advanced filtering for date range, origin, customer, "
"cashier, and search. Supports viewing web orders for return scenarios. "
"Default: today's orders from this terminal only. Search mode: When 'search' "
"is provided, date/origin/cashier filters are bypassed to find any order by "
"number, customer name, email, or phone. Requires staff authentication and "
"valid POS license."
msgstr ""
"根據日期範圍、來源、客戶、收銀員和搜尋條件進行高階過濾來返回訂單。支援查看退貨場景的網頁訂單。預設：僅顯示此終端今天的訂單。搜尋模式：當提供 "
"'search' 時，會跳過日期/來源/收銀員過濾條件，以訂單號、客戶名稱、電子郵件或電話來查找任何訂單。需要員工驗證和有效的 POS 授權。"

msgid ""
"Start date for range filter (ISO format, default: today). Ignored when "
"search is provided."
msgstr "範圍過濾的起始日期（ISO 格式，預設：今天）。當提供搜尋時會忽略。"

msgid ""
"End date for range filter (ISO format, default: today). Ignored when search "
"is provided."
msgstr "範圍過濾的結束日期（ISO 格式，預設：今天）。當提供搜尋時會忽略。"

msgid ""
"Order origin filter: this_terminal (default), all_pos, all (includes web). "
"Ignored when search is provided."
msgstr "訂單來源過濾器：this_terminal（預設）、all_pos、all（包含網頁）。當提供搜尋時會忽略此過濾器。"

msgid "Filter by customer user ID. Ignored when search is provided."
msgstr "依客戶用戶 ID 篩選。當提供搜尋時會忽略。"

msgid "Filter by cashier staff ID. Ignored when search is provided."
msgstr "依收銀員員工 ID 篩選。當提供搜尋時會忽略。"

msgid ""
"Search across ALL orders by order number, customer name, email, or phone. "
"Bypasses date/origin filters."
msgstr "透過訂單編號、客戶姓名、電子郵件或電話搜尋所有訂單。跳過日期/來源過濾器。"

msgid "Filter by order status (applies in both modes)"
msgstr "依訂單狀態篩選（兩種模式均適用）"

msgid "Get order details"
msgstr "取得訂單詳情"

msgid ""
"Returns full order details including items and payment breakdown. Supports "
"both POS and web orders (for return scenarios). Requires staff "
"authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr "返回完整的訂單詳情，包括商品和付款明細。支援POS和網頁訂單（用於退貨場景）。需要員工驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "Get receipt data for printing"
msgstr "取得用於列印的收據資料"

msgid ""
"Returns receipt-formatted data for a POS order including store info, items, "
"payments, and footer text. Designed for ESC/POS thermal printers. Requires "
"staff authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr ""
"返回 POS 訂單的收據格式資料，包含商店資訊、商品、付款和頁尾文字。專為 ESC/POS 熱感應印表機設計。需要員工驗證和有效的 POS 授權許可。"

msgid "Process order refund"
msgstr "處理訂單退款"

msgid ""
"Process a full or partial refund for a POS order. For partial refunds, "
"specify the items and quantities to refund. Creates a Refund record and "
"updates the order and shift totals. Requires an open shift on the terminal. "
"Requires staff authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr ""
"處理 POS "
"訂單的全額或部分退款。對於部分退款，請指定要退款的商品和數量。會建立退款記錄並更新訂單和班次總額。需要終端機上有開啟的班次。需要員工驗證和有效的 POS"
" 授權許可。"

msgid "Refund processed successfully"
msgstr "退款處理成功"

msgid "Invalid refund request or order already refunded"
msgstr "無效的退款請求或訂單已退款"

msgid "Void a POS order"
msgstr "作廢POS訂單"

msgid ""
"Cancel a POS order from the current shift. Only orders placed during the "
"current open shift can be voided. This creates a full refund and reverses "
"all payment and inventory changes. Requires an open shift on the terminal. "
"Requires staff authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr ""
"取消當前班次的POS訂單。只有在當前開放班次中下達的訂單才能取消。這會產生完整的退款並撤銷所有付款和庫存更改。需要終端機上有開放的班次。需要員工驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "Order voided successfully"
msgstr "訂單作廢成功"

msgid "Order cannot be voided (not from current shift)"
msgstr "無法取消訂單（非當前班次產生的訂單）"

msgid "List POS cashiers"
msgstr "列出POS收銀員"

msgid ""
"Returns list of staff members who have processed POS orders. Used to "
"populate the cashier filter dropdown. Requires staff authentication and "
"valid POS license."
msgstr "返回已處理POS訂單的員工清單。用於填充收銀員過濾下拉選單。需要員工驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "List of cashiers"
msgstr "收銀員清單"

msgid "Send digital receipt"
msgstr "發送數位收據"

msgid ""
"Send a digital receipt to the customer via email, SMS, or WhatsApp. The "
"receipt is sent asynchronously via Celery task. Requires staff "
"authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr "透過電子郵件、簡訊或WhatsApp向客戶發送數位收據。收據會透過Celery任務異步發送。需要員工驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "Receipt queued for sending"
msgstr "收據已排隊發送"

msgid "Get receipt sending status"
msgstr "取得收據發送狀態"

msgid ""
"Check which digital receipts have been sent for an order. Returns timestamps"
" for email and SMS/WhatsApp deliveries."
msgstr "檢查某筆訂單已發送哪些數位收據。會返回電子郵件和簡訊/WhatsApp發送的時間戳記。"

msgid "Receipt status"
msgstr "收據狀態"

msgid "Get current shift summary"
msgstr "取得當前班次摘要"

msgid ""
"Returns the open shift summary for the current cashier on the terminal, "
"including totals, transaction count, and payment method breakdown. Returns "
"null shift if no shift is open. Requires staff authentication and valid POS "
"license."
msgstr ""
"返回終端機上當前收銀員的當前班次摘要，包括總額、交易數量和支付方式細分。如果沒有開啟班次，則返回 null。需要員工驗證和有效的 POS 授權。"

msgid "Open a new shift"
msgstr "開啟新班次"

msgid ""
"Start a new shift on the terminal. Only one open shift is allowed per "
"terminal at any time. Records the opening cash amount. Requires staff "
"authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr "在終端機上開始新的班次。每次只能在每個終端機上開啟一個班次。記錄開班時的現金金額。需要員工驗證和有效的 POS 授權。"

msgid "Invalid opening cash amount"
msgstr "開班次現金金額無效"

msgid "A shift is already open on this terminal"
msgstr "此終端機上已有開啟的班次"

msgid "Close current shift"
msgstr "結束當前班次"

msgid ""
"Close the current open shift. Records the closing cash amount and calculates"
" the expected vs actual cash difference. Requires staff authentication and "
"valid POS license."
msgstr "關閉目前開啟的班次。記錄結班時的現金金額，並計算預期與實際現金的差額。需要員工驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "Record cash movement"
msgstr "記錄現金流動"

msgid ""
"Record a cash-in or cash-out movement during the shift. Examples: adding "
"float, removing for deposit, petty cash. Requires an open shift on the "
"terminal. Requires staff authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr ""
"在班次期間記錄現金收入或支出的動作。範例：增加浮動現金、移除以進行存款、零用現金。需要終端機上開啟的班次。需要員工驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "Cash movement recorded"
msgstr "現金流動已記錄"

msgid "Invalid movement data"
msgstr "無效的流動資料"

msgid "Get daily sales report"
msgstr "取得每日銷售報告"

msgid ""
"Returns an aggregated daily sales report for the terminal including totals, "
"transaction count, average transaction value, and payment method breakdown. "
"Requires staff authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr "返回終端的聚合每日銷售報告，包括總額、交易數量、平均交易金額和支付方式細分。需要員工驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "Report date (ISO format, default: today)"
msgstr "報告日期（ISO 格式，預設：今天）"

msgid "Get top selling products"
msgstr "取得銷量最高的產品"

msgid ""
"Returns the top selling products for the terminal on a given date, ranked by"
" quantity sold. Requires staff authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr "返回指定日期終端的熱銷產品，按銷售數量排序。需要員工驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "Number of products to return (default: 10, max: 50)"
msgstr "要返回的產品數量（預設：10，最多：50）"

msgid "Sync products since timestamp"
msgstr "自時間戳記同步產品"

msgid ""
"Returns products that have been created or updated since the given "
"timestamp. Used for incremental product sync to the POS terminal's local "
"database. Returns a sync_token for the next sync request. Requires staff "
"authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr ""
"自指定時間戳記以來已建立或更新的產品。用於將產品逐步同步到POS終端的本地資料庫。會傳回用於下一次同步請求的sync_token。需要員工驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "ISO timestamp to fetch changes since. Omit for full sync."
msgstr "用來取得自該時間戳之後變更的 ISO 時間戳。若要完整同步，請省略此欄位。"

msgid "Items per page (default: 100, max: 200)"
msgstr "每頁項目數（預設：100，最大：200）"

msgid "Sync customers since timestamp"
msgstr "自時間戳記同步顧客"

msgid ""
"Returns customers that have been created or have placed orders since the "
"given timestamp. Used for offline customer lookup. Requires staff "
"authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr "自指定時間戳記以來已建立或下過訂單的客戶。用於離線客戶查詢。需要員工驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "Customer sync data"
msgstr "顧客同步資料"

msgid "Upload offline transactions"
msgstr "上傳離線交易"

msgid ""
"Batch upload transactions that were processed while the terminal was "
"offline. Each transaction creates an Order with items and payments. Uses "
"local_id for idempotency -- duplicate uploads are detected and skipped. "
"Requires staff authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr ""
"批次上傳在終端機離線期間處理的交易。每個交易會創建一個包含商品和付款的訂單。使用 local_id 來確保 idempotency —— "
"會檢測並跳過重複上傳。需要員工驗證和有效的 POS 授權。"

msgid "Upload results with success/failure per transaction"
msgstr "上傳每個交易的成功/失敗結果"

msgid "Get sync status"
msgstr "取得同步狀態"

msgid ""
"Returns the current server time and database counts for sync planning. "
"Requires staff authentication and valid POS license."
msgstr "返回目前伺服器時間和資料庫數量，用於同步規劃。需要員工驗證和有效的 POS 授權。"

msgid "Get sync version info"
msgstr "取得同步版本資訊"

msgid ""
"Returns API version and data schema version for client compatibility checks."
" Clients should clear and resync when schema version increases."
msgstr "返回 API 版本和數據結構版本，用於客戶端兼容性檢查。當結構版本增加時，客戶端應清除並重新同步。"

msgid "Version information"
msgstr "版本資訊"

msgid "Upload offline stock adjustments"
msgstr "上傳離線庫存調整"

msgid ""
"Batch upload stock adjustments that were queued while the terminal was "
"offline. Each adjustment uses an idempotency key to prevent duplicates. "
"Requires staff authentication, valid POS license, and stock adjustment "
"permission."
msgstr ""
"批量上傳在終端離線時排隊的庫存調整。每個調整使用 idempotency 金鑰以防止重複。需要員工驗證、有效的 POS 授權許可證和庫存調整權限。"

msgid "Upload results with success/failure per adjustment"
msgstr "上傳每個調整的成功/失敗結果"

msgid "POS license or permission required"
msgstr "需要 POS 授權或權限"

msgid "Sync orders for offline cache"
msgstr "為離線緩存同步訂單"

msgid ""
"Returns orders for offline caching on the POS terminal. POS orders are "
"prioritised over web orders up to the terminal's sync limit. Supports delta "
"sync via the 'since' parameter. Requires staff authentication and valid POS "
"license."
msgstr ""
"在POS終端機上進行離線緩存的訂單。POS訂單優先於網頁訂單，直到終端機的同步限制。支援透過 'since' "
"參數進行增量同步。需要員工驗證和有效的POS許可證。"

msgid "ISO timestamp for delta sync. Omit for full sync."
msgstr "用於增量同步的ISO時間戳。省略以執行完整同步。"

msgid "Register POS terminal"
msgstr "註冊 POS 端點"

msgid ""
"Register a new device as a POS terminal using a pairing code. The pairing "
"code is generated in the admin panel when creating a terminal."
msgstr "使用配對碼將新設備註冊為POS終端機。配對碼在創建終端機時於管理面板中生成。"

msgid "Terminal registered successfully, returns terminal config"
msgstr "終端機註冊成功，返回終端機配置"

msgid "Invalid or expired pairing code"
msgstr "無效或過期的配對碼"

msgid "Get terminal configuration"
msgstr "取得終端機設定"

msgid ""
"Returns the current terminal's configuration including hardware settings."
msgstr "返回當前終端機的配置，包括硬體設置。"

msgid "Terminal heartbeat"
msgstr "終端機心跳"

msgid "Report that the terminal is online. Should be called every 60 seconds."
msgstr "報告終端機為在線狀態。應每 60 秒呼叫一次。"

msgid "Heartbeat recorded"
msgstr "心跳已記錄"

msgid "Get receipt template"
msgstr "取得收據範本"

msgid ""
"Returns the receipt template for the terminal's warehouse. Falls back to the"
" default template (no warehouse assigned) if the warehouse has no specific "
"template. Returns sensible defaults if no template exists at all."
msgstr "返回終端倉庫的收據模板。如果倉庫沒有特定模板，則回退到預設模板（未指定倉庫）。如果完全沒有模板，則返回合理的預設值。"

msgid "Receipt template data"
msgstr "收據範本資料"

msgid "Get promo slides"
msgstr "取得促銷幻燈片"

msgid ""
"Returns promotional slides for the terminal's warehouse. Slides are "
"displayed on the customer-facing display during idle periods."
msgstr "返回終端倉庫的促銷幻燈片。幻燈片會在客戶面對的顯示器閒置期間顯示。"

msgid "List of promo slides with image URLs"
msgstr "促銷幻燈片列表，包含圖片 URL"

msgid "Generate display pairing code"
msgstr "生成顯示配對碼"

msgid ""
"Generate a short-lived 6-digit pairing code for customer display "
"authentication. The code expires after 5 minutes and can only be used once. "
"Generating a new code invalidates any existing unused codes for this "
"terminal."
msgstr "為客戶顯示驗證生成一個短暫有效的6位配對碼。該碼5分鐘後過期，且只能使用一次。生成新碼將使此終端機上所有未使用的現有碼失效。"

msgid "Pairing code generated"
msgstr "已生成配對碼"

msgid "List managers for unlock override"
msgstr "列出用於解除鎖定的管理員"

msgid ""
"Return list of managers (id and name) for the manager override unlock flow."
msgstr "返回管理員列表（id 和姓名），用於管理員覆蓋解鎖流程。"

msgid "List of managers"
msgstr "管理員列表"

msgid "Verify unlock PIN"
msgstr "驗證解除鎖定的PIN碼"

msgid ""
"Verify a cashier or manager PIN to unlock the terminal. After 3 failed "
"attempts, only manager PIN will be accepted. All attempts are logged for "
"audit purposes."
msgstr "驗證出納員或經理的PIN碼以解鎖終端機。在3次失敗嘗試後，僅接受經理PIN碼。所有嘗試都會被記錄以供審計。"

msgid "PIN verified successfully"
msgstr "PIN碼驗證成功"

msgid "Invalid PIN"
msgstr "無效的PIN碼"

msgid "Log terminal lock event"
msgstr "記錄終端鎖定事件"

msgid ""
"Log when a terminal is locked (manually or via auto-lock timeout). This "
"endpoint is for audit logging only and does not change terminal state."
msgstr "當終端被鎖定時（手動或通過自動鎖定超時）進行記錄。此端點僅用於審計日誌，不會改變終端狀態。"

msgid "Event logged successfully"
msgstr "事件已成功記錄"

msgid "Invalid event type"
msgstr "無效的事件類型"

msgid "Verify unlock card"
msgstr "驗證解鎖卡片"

msgid ""
"Verify a staff ID card swipe to unlock the terminal. Card data is hashed and"
" compared against stored card hashes. After 3 failed PIN attempts, only "
"manager cards are accepted."
msgstr "驗證員工 ID 卡刷卡以解鎖終端。卡片資料會進行雜湊處理，並與儲存的卡片雜湊進行比對。在 3 次 PIN 確認失敗後，僅接受管理員卡片。"

msgid "Card verified successfully"
msgstr "卡片已成功驗證"

msgid "Card not recognized"
msgstr "卡片無法識別"

msgid "Register staff unlock card"
msgstr "註冊員工解鎖卡片"

msgid "Register a card swipe for the current user's quick terminal unlock."
msgstr "為當前用戶的快速終端機解鎖註冊刷卡。"

msgid "Card registered successfully"
msgstr "卡片註冊成功"

msgid "Card already registered to another user"
msgstr "此卡已註冊至其他用戶"

msgid "Remove staff unlock card"
msgstr "移除員工解鎖卡片"

msgid "Remove the current user's registered unlock card."
msgstr "移除當前用戶註冊的解鎖卡片。"

msgid "Card removed successfully"
msgstr "卡片移除成功"

msgid "Set cashier PIN"
msgstr "設定收銀員PIN碼"

msgid ""
"Set or update the current user's cashier PIN for terminal lock/unlock. PIN "
"must be 4-6 digits. Both pin and pin_confirm must match."
msgstr ""
"設定或更新目前用戶的收銀員 PIN 碼，用於終端機鎖定/解鎖。PIN 碼必須為 4 到 6 位數字。PIN 和 pin_confirm 必須一致。"

msgid "PIN set successfully"
msgstr "PIN 設置成功"

msgid "Get terminal provider config"
msgstr "取得終端機供應商設定"

msgid ""
"Returns the terminal provider configuration for the current terminal, "
"including the integration mode (sdk, cloud, or manual) and connected reader "
"details. Used by the POS frontend on startup to determine if an integrated "
"card reader is available and which payment flow to use."
msgstr ""
"返回目前終端機的終端機供應商配置，包括整合模式（sdk、cloud 或 manual）和連接的讀卡器詳細資訊。用於 POS "
"前端啟動時判斷是否可用整合式讀卡器，以及使用哪種付款流程。"

msgid "Create connection token"
msgstr "建立連線憑證"

msgid ""
"Creates a short-lived connection token for SDK-mode terminal providers (e.g."
" Stripe Terminal JS SDK). The frontend calls this endpoint when initializing"
" the SDK to establish a direct connection with the reader. SDK only. Cloud "
"providers do not use connection tokens. Returns 400 if the provider does not"
" support SDK tokens."
msgstr ""
"為 SDK 模式終端機供應商創建一個短暫有效的連接令牌（例如 Stripe Terminal JS SDK）。前端在初始化 SDK "
"時呼叫此端點，以與讀卡器建立直接連接。僅限 SDK 使用。雲端供應商不使用連接令牌。如果供應商不支援 SDK 令牌，則返回 400。"

msgid "List card readers"
msgstr "列出卡片讀卡器"

msgid ""
"List available card readers from the terminal provider. Works for both SDK-"
"mode and cloud-mode providers. Each reader object contains: id, label, type,"
" serial_number, and status."
msgstr "從終端機提供商列出可用的卡片讀取器。適用於 SDK 模式和雲端模式的提供商。每個讀取器物件包含：id、標籤、類型、序列號和狀態。"

msgid "Create payment intent for terminal"
msgstr "為終端機建立付款意圖"

msgid ""
"Creates a PaymentIntent for card_present collection on the terminal reader. "
"The frontend uses the returned client_secret to collect payment via the SDK."
" SDK only. Cloud providers should use initiate-cloud-payment. If currency is"
" omitted, defaults to the terminal's configured currency."
msgstr ""
"為終端機讀取器上的 card_present 收集創建 PaymentIntent。前端使用返回的 client_secret 透過 SDK "
"收集付款。僅限 SDK。雲端提供商應使用 initiate-cloud-payment。如果省略貨幣，預設為終端機設定的貨幣。"

msgid "Capture/verify terminal payment"
msgstr "捕獲/驗證終端機付款"

msgid ""
"Verifies that a PaymentIntent was successfully processed on the terminal "
"reader and returns card details (brand, last4) from the provider. SDK only."
msgstr "驗證付款意圖已在終端機讀卡器上成功處理，並從提供商返回卡片詳情（品牌、後四位數字）。僅限 SDK 使用。"

msgid "Cancel terminal payment"
msgstr "取消終端機付款"

msgid ""
"Cancel a pending PaymentIntent on the terminal reader (e.g. customer "
"cancelled). SDK only. Cloud providers should use cancel-cloud-payment."
msgstr "在終端機讀卡器上取消待處理的付款意圖（例如客戶取消）。僅限 SDK 使用。雲端提供商應使用 cancel-cloud-payment。"

msgid "Initiate cloud payment on reader"
msgstr "在讀卡機上啟動雲端付款"

msgid ""
"Sends a payment request to a card reader via the provider's cloud API. For "
"cloud-mode terminal providers only (Adyen, Square, SumUp, Zettle). Cloud "
"only. Returns 400 if provider uses SDK mode. If currency is omitted, "
"defaults to the terminal's configured currency."
msgstr ""
"透過供應商的雲端 API "
"向卡片讀取器發送付款請求。僅適用於雲端模式的終端機供應商（Adyen、Square、SumUp、Zettle）。僅限雲端。如果供應商使用 SDK "
"模式，則會返回 400。如果未指定貨幣，則預設為終端機設定的貨幣。"

msgid "Check cloud payment status"
msgstr "檢查雲端付款狀態"

msgid ""
"Poll the status of a cloud-initiated payment. Returns the current status: "
"pending, succeeded, failed, or canceled. When status is 'succeeded', the "
"response includes card_brand, last4, and the provider payment_id. When "
"'canceled', includes cancel_reason. Frontend should poll every 2 seconds "
"until status is no longer 'pending'."
msgstr ""
"輪詢雲端啟動付款的狀態。返回目前狀態：pending（待處理）、succeeded（成功）、failed（失敗）或 canceled（已取消）。當狀態為"
" 'succeeded' 時，回應包含 card_brand、last4 和供應商 payment_id。當狀態為 'canceled' 時，包含 "
"cancel_reason。前端應每隔 2 秒輪詢，直到狀態不再是 'pending'。"

msgid "Provider-specific transaction ID returned by initiate-cloud-payment"
msgstr "由啟動雲端付款返回的特定供應商交易 ID"

msgid "Cancel cloud payment"
msgstr "取消雲端付款"

msgid ""
"Cancel a pending cloud-initiated payment on the reader. Cloud only. Behavior"
" varies by provider."
msgstr "在讀卡器上取消待處理的雲端啟動付款。僅限雲端。行為因供應商而異。"

msgid "Begin WebAuthn registration"
msgstr "開始 WebAuthn 註冊"

msgid ""
"Generate registration options for biometric enrollment. Returns challenge "
"and credential creation options."
msgstr "產生生物特徵註冊選項。返回挑戰和憑證創建選項。"

msgid "Registration options"
msgstr "註冊選項"

msgid "Complete WebAuthn registration"
msgstr "完成 WebAuthn 註冊"

msgid "Verify attestation and store credential for biometric unlock."
msgstr "驗證認證並儲存生物特徵解鎖憑證。"

msgid "Credential registered"
msgstr "憑證已註冊"

msgid "Verification failed"
msgstr "驗證失敗"

msgid "Begin WebAuthn authentication"
msgstr "開始 WebAuthn 驗證"

msgid ""
"Generate authentication challenge for biometric unlock. Returns "
"allowCredentials for the locked-by user and all managers. If failed_attempts"
" >= 3, only manager credentials are included."
msgstr ""
"產生生物特徵解鎖的驗證挑戰。返回被鎖定用戶和所有管理員的 allowCredentials。如果 failed_attempts >= "
"3，則僅包含管理員憑證。"

msgid "Authentication options"
msgstr "驗證選項"

msgid "No credentials registered"
msgstr "未註冊憑證"

msgid "Complete WebAuthn authentication"
msgstr "完成 WebAuthn 認證"

msgid "Verify biometric assertion and unlock terminal."
msgstr "驗證生物特徵斷言並解鎖終端。"

msgid "Authentication successful"
msgstr "認證成功"
